			<item>
				<title>Tools of the trade</title>
				<description>&lt;p&gt;There are a number of tools I find I rely on throught out the day. My intention is to make a list of them and talk about the pros and cons for each one in a separate post. My hope is that by sharing my experience with each one, I can better see for myself why I like one tool over another and also share why I may or may not be considering moving to another tool.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So, the list:&lt;/p&gt;

